1. *Koji* dan je danas? (Which day is it today?)
2. On je čuo da je *koji* čovek izgubio posao. (He heard that some man had lost his job.)
3. Ona je videla *koju* sliku? (She saw which picture?)
4. On je tražio *koje* knjige imamo? (He was asking which books we have?)
5. *Koje* boje? (Which colours?)
6. *Kojim* putem ćemo ići? (Which way will we go?)